Fourth Department,

March, 1949.

(March 2, 1949.) In the Matter of the Second Intermediate Accounting of James H. Slocum et al., as Trustees under the Will of Daniel M. Edwards, Deceased, Respondents. Dorothy L. Edwards, as Ancillary Committee of Walker E. Edwards, an Incompetent, and as General Guardian of Flora B. Edwards and Others, Infants, Appellant.

Present — Taylor, P. J., McCurn, Love, Vaughan and Piper, JJ.
